<number box="[1595,1603,2343,2363]" pageId="1" pageNumber="146" value="3.0">3</number>
, white pilose. Antenna dark reddish brown, black pilose; arista yellow; antennal ratio: 
<number box="[344,384,2415,2443]" pageId="1" pageNumber="146" value="1.7">1.7</number>
&quot; 1.0:1.0: 
<number box="[534,579,2415,2443]" pageId="1" pageNumber="146" value="1.3">1.3</number>
